    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>prosciutto slices</strong> to a plate and put in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 4-5 min, then set aside until serving to dry and crisp up – this is your <strong>crispy prosciutto</strong></p><p>Tip: Check your prosciutto slices every 30 secs to prevent them from burning, as microwave temperatures vary!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1663669611305-x200.jpg",
