            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1663669616058-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>spinach & ricotta ravioli</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the ravioli for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> cooked spinach & ricotta ravioli</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1663669620489-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1663669620489-x400.jpg",
