            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Caprese-style sauce with spinach & ricotta ravioli</strong> and top with the<strong> crispy prosciutto</strong> and <strong>remaining chopped basil</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and<strong> </strong>a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
